xwikidoc.content: <sdumitriu> has quit 15:31 <phenotips_org> has joined #phenotips 15:38 <akats> has quit 15:54 <akats> has joined #phenotips 16:20 <akats> Does age of onset have to be changed in PatientSheetCode? 16:20 <akats> .xml 16:21 <sdumitriu1> Checking 16:22 <sdumitriu1> No 16:22 <sdumitriu1> That one is for individual onsets set for selected phenotypes 16:22 <akats> So then I would assume that it doesn't have to be changed in UIX_Field_age_of_onset? 16:23 <sdumitriu1> Also be careful in Export, there are two kinds of fields 16:23 <sdumitriu1> One age_of_onset is in phenotype metadata processing, and shouldn't be changed 16:23 <sdumitriu1> Hm, actually just this one is explicitly mentioned 16:23 <sdumitriu1> So Export shouldn't be changed 16:24 <sdumitriu1> The UIX has to be changed 16:24 <akats> Not everywhere though right? 16:50 <akats> Pushed 713. Seems to work. But then again, I don't know how to do extensive testing with this kind of change. 16:50 <sdumitriu1> OK, I'll check 17:06 <akats> and pushed 712 17:20 <akats> around what time do you think you'll be here tomorrow 17:20 <sdumitriu1> 11 17:28 <akats> if you have time right now and have a next task at hand for me, would you want to introduce me to it? 17:29 <sdumitriu1> Would you like some JavaScript? 17:30 <akats> Got nothing against that 17:36 <akats> has quit 20:39 <sdumitriu> has joined #phenotips
